<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
<title>登录 | 新浪办公网接入认证系统</title>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

<link rel="icon" href="/media/images/vdun/favicon.ico"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/media/css/vdun/d-reset.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/media/css/vdun/login.css">

<script type="text/javascript" src="/media/js/vdun/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/media/js/vdun/jquery.cookie.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="/media/js/vdun/jquery.qrcode.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/media/js/vdun/vdun_qrcode.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="/media/js/vdun/login.js"></script>

<script>
    $.vdun_qrcode({
        // 分配的APPID
        appid: 1020,
        // 二维码大小
        size: 215,
        // 是否显示鼠标放置二维码上后的帮助图片
        help: true,
        // 是否显示二维码下面的推送
        push: true,

        scanned_callback: function (sid) {
            $("#vdun-push").hide();
            $(".num-succ").css("visibility","visible").show();
        },

        // 点击确认验证后回调的函数，sid会在回调时自动提供
        authed_callback: function (sid) {
            //请求本地服务器进行验证
            $.get('/vdun_login', {sid: sid}).done(function(r) {
                if(r.status == 0){
                   location.href="http://10.210.12.253/loading/";
                }else{
                   console.log(JSON.stringify(r));
                }
            });
        }
    });
</script>

</head>

<body>
<div id="top-tip"></div>
<div class="login-main">
    <!--top-->
    <div class="login-top">
        <p class="top-tit">Network Access System</p>
        <p class="tit-con">新浪办公网认证系统</p>
    </div>

    <div class="login-content clearfix">
        <div class="two-num">
            <p class="num-txt">扫描二维码登录</p>
            <div id="vdun-qrcode"></div>
            <p class="num-succ">扫描成功，请用手机确认登录</p>
        </div>

        <div class="line"><img src="../media/images/vdun/login-line.png"/></div>

        <div class="con-login">
            <form action='/' method="post" id="login-form">
                <p class="input-tit">
                    <input type="hidden" id="login-type" name="login_type" value="radius"/>
                    <!-- 加类login-cur字体为蓝色-->
                    <span id="opt-radius">动态口令登录</span>
                    <span id="opt-divider">|</span>
                    <span id="opt-ldap">邮箱帐号登录</span>
                </p>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="name" placeholder="用户名"/>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="动态口令"/>
                <button id="submit" class="login-btn">登&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;录</button>
                <div id="input-extra">
                    <p class="login-way">
                        <span id="submit-guest">来宾登录</span>
                        <span id="help" class="no-marg">帮助说明</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div id="error-tip">
                    <span id="error-msg"></span>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div> 

    <div class="login-bot">
        <p>Copyright &copy; 2010-2015 SINA.&nbsp;All Rights Reserved.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;支持电话：5666</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="custom" id="help-content">
    <div id="help-title">办公网认证系统帮助</div>
    <hr/>
    <div id="help-main">
     登录账号为邮箱前缀，来宾登陆无需账号密码:
     <ol>
         <li>使用<strong>动态口令登录</strong>，将获得自己部门已申请过的权限</li>
         <li>使用<strong>邮箱密码登录</strong>，只有公共办公权限，供临时使用</li>
         <li>使用<strong>来宾登录</strong>，只能访问公共互联网</li>
     </ol>
     <strong>*注意事项*:</strong>
     <ol>
         <li><strong>邮箱登录</strong>与<strong>来宾登录</strong>不能使用以下应用：</li>
         <ul>
             <li>网络P2P下载，P2P视频，网络电视等应用</li>
             <li>所有网络游戏</li>
             <li>所有股票软件</li>
         </ul>
         <li>请尽量使用动态口令登录，如丢失或忘带卡，可用手机认证（账号为邮箱全称）</li>
         <li>以来宾权限登录后，想切换回部门办公权限，请回到<a href="http://10.210.12.253">本页面</a>重新登录。</li>
     </ol>
    </div>
    <hr/>
    <div id="help-foot">By SinaSec</div>
</div>
<div id="layer"> </div>
</body>
</html>
